text: The People Party () or Party of Nationals is a political party in South Korea. Its color is orange. The party was founded by Ahn Cheol-soo in February 2020, after leaving the Bareunmirae Party. It has the same name as the People Party, which was also founded by Ahn and existed from 2016 to 2018. ==Notes== ==References== Category:Political parties in South Korea
title: People Party (South Korea)
